data.title: Scream VI on Paramount+: Ghostface terrorizes New York with Melissa Barrera and Jenna Ortega
data.meta_description: Scream VI, a horror film directed by Matt Bettinelli-Olpin and Tyler Gillett, starring Melissa Barrera, Jenna Ortega and Courteney Cox, arrives on Paramount+ on August 8, 2024. Released in cinemas on March 8, 2023, this sixth opus in the Scream franchise takes Ghostface's terror to the streets of New York.
data.text:
Scream VI is the latest installment in the celebrated horror saga (another opus has been announced for 2025), directed by Matt Bettinelli-Olpin and Tyler Gillett, known for their work on Scream 2022 and Wedding Nightmare. With a script by James Vanderbilt and Guy Busick, the film features a talented cast including Melissa Barrera(In the Heights), Jenna Ortega(Wednesday) and Courteney Cox(Friends). Scream VI promises to redefine fear by transporting the iconic Ghostface killer to the sprawling metropolis of New York.

After wreaking havoc in Woodsboro, on the Windsor campus and in Hollywood studios, Ghostface decides to strike in the Big Apple. But in a city as vast as New York, no one will hear you scream... The survivors of Ghostface's previous attacks, Sam (Melissa Barrera) and Tara Carpenter (Jenna Ortega), along with Gale Weathers (Courteney Cox), must once again face their worst nightmares. As Ghostface stalks his new victims across the city, tension mounts and the streets of New York become a veritable battlefield, where every corner can conceal a deadly danger.

Scream VI is aimed at horror film enthusiasts and long-time fans of the Scream franchise. The film stands out for its unprecedented urban setting, bringing a new dimension of terror to the series. Audiences who enjoyed films like Halloween and The Texas Chainsaw Massacre will find Scream VI a thrilling and frightening experience. The performances of Melissa Barrera and Jenna Ortega, combined with the expert direction of Bettinelli-Olpin and Gillett, guarantee a perfect blend of suspense, thrills and nostalgia for fans of the saga.

Scream VI is a horror film that transports the iconic terror of Ghostface to the bustling streets of New York. Available on Paramount+ from August 8, 2024, the film offers a fresh perspective on a legendary franchise, combining classic slasher elements with a modern urban setting. Whether you're a long-time Scream fan or a horror movie buff looking for some intense thrills, Scream VI promises to keep you on the edge of your seat from start to finish.
